tags.name: Elmstead Woods
tags.wheelchair:description: Step free access to platform 4 for services away from London from Station Approach. There is no step free access to Platform 1, 2 or 3. No step free interchange between platforms.

tags.name: Norwood Junction
tags.wheelchair:description: To access any platforms except platform 1 there is only stair access. There are about 15 stairs to access the platforms.

tags.name: Lower Sydenham
tags.wheelchair:description: Step Free to both platforms, No step free interchange between platforms.

tags.name: New Beckenham
tags.wheelchair:description: Step free access to both platforms. No step free interchange between platforms.

tags.name: Clock House
tags.wheelchair:description: Step free access to platform 2 for services away from London via Clock House Road. There is no step free access to Platform 1.

tags.name: Eden Park
tags.wheelchair:description: Step free access to platform 1 for services to London. There is no step free access to Platform 2.Only step access to platform 2 for services away from London. No step free interchange between platforms.

tags.name: Anerley
tags.wheelchair:description: Step-free from streets to platforms on both sides. Steps and footbridge between platforms.

tags.name: Penge East
tags.wheelchair:description: Step free access to platform 1 from main entrance. Step free access to platform 2 via Lindon Grove - No step free interchange between platforms but stepped access via station footbridge is available.

tags.name: Bromley South
tags.wheelchair:description: Access from platform to train by manual boarding ramp

tags.name: Beckenham Hill
tags.wheelchair:description: Step-free platform interchange requires a 400m+ journey via street. Access from platform to train by manual boarding ramp.

tags.name: Ravensbourne
tags.wheelchair:description: Step-free southbound only. Access from platform to train by manual boarding ramp.

tags.defibrillator:location: On the wall on platform 1, aside the information desk

tags.name: Hayes
tags.wheelchair:description: Short ramp access from car park to station entrance. Step free access to these terminal platform from station entrance via short steep ramp.

tags.name: Sundridge Park
tags.wheelchair:description: Step free access available to platform 2 for services to Bromley North via gate from side path. There is no step free access to Platform 1.
